title: Russian for adults - Charles Duff and Dmitri Makaroff (learn rus
description:
The best book I ever found to learn Russian.

All purposes - Russian for Adults
A comprehensive course on modern lines, simplified for absolute beignners, designed for self-tuition, private tuition or class use.
By Charles Duff and Dmitri Makaroff

The English Universities Press Limited. First Printed 1962.

I scanned it originally only to have a *backup* of the book, if I ever lost it.
